response.overview: The first part of this "art study" film looks at a woman going through different motions repeatedly which she then later does in the buff, while artists paint her. It then shows a woman on the beach doing gymnastics motions. It ends with the “Featurette” which looks at a short story of a man and woman falling for each other after they both find each other naked in the woods and look for the woman’s clothes, which have hilariously been stolen by an amateur detective.
response.title: Art Models
